high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the left side of the stove.
Turn around and go left to stand in front of the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the pan back up again.
Turn around and go right to stand in front of the stove again.
Put the pan on the back right side of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and move right and then locate the stove.
Pick up the pan from the back left burner of the stove.
Hold the pan and turn around, then left to locate the sink.
Place the pan in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the pan.
Carry the pan and turn to the left to find the stove on the right.
Place the pan on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a pan and place it on the stove.

high_descs: Turn the opposite direction and cross the kitchen to the stove.
Pick up the skillet from the back left burner.
Go to the sink that is slightly behind you to your right.
Wash the skillet in the sink.
Put the skillet on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned skillet on a stovetop.
